meaningOFSYMBOLE:
h: depth of section

     b: width of section

     d: depth of straight portion of web

     r, r1: radius of root fillet

     r2: toe radius

     t: thickness

     tf: flange thickness

     tw: web thickness

     A: area of section

     I: second moment of area

     i: radius of gyration

     IT: torsion constant

     Iw: warping constant

     Iyz: centrifugal moment

     G: mass per unit length

     Wel: elastic section modulus ρa unit mass of steel

     Wpl: plastic section modulus

     w: distance of extreme fibre to minor v-axis

     v: distance of extreme fibre to major u-axis

     Ym: shear center
meaningOFSYMBOLEWelded:
h: depth of section

     wPlate: width of plate

     tPlate: thickness of plate

     wtf: width of top flange

     ttf: thickness of top flange

     wbf: width of bottom flange

     tbf: thickness of bottom flange

     d: depth of straight portion of web

     tw: web thickness

     e: distance of extreme fibre to minor y-axis

     A: area of section

     I: second moment of area

     i: radius of gyration

     G: mass per unit length

     Wel: elastic section modulus ρa unit mass of steel

     Wpl: plastic section modulus
